    "46984072": {
      "title": "The health economics of bladder cancer: a comprehensive review of the published literature",
      "abstract": "The aim of this paper was to conduct a critical systematic review of the available literature on the clinical and economic burden of bladder cancer in developed countries, with a focus on the cost effectiveness of interventions aimed at reducing that burden."
